 "remarks": "Wake up each morning to breathtaking 270-degree views of Long Island Sound, where sailboats, paddleboarders, and ever-changing waterfront activity create a stunning backdrop to everyday life. Located in the heart of Saugatuck, this beautifully renovated home blends coastal charm with modern convenience.  Thoughtfully reimagined by a talented local photographer with an eye for design, the home features a stylish new kitchen, beautifully updated baths, and hardwood floors throughout. Outside, a private, low-maintenance yard offers the perfect setting to relax and unwind, allowing more time to enjoy the waterfront lifestyle and less time spent on upkeep. A private dock accommodates a small boat, making it easy to get out on the water and fully embrace this exceptional coastal setting. Conveniently located just minutes from the train, offering an easy and efficient commute to New York City.",
